<P>

<s docid="LA020190-0053" num="56"> ASTRONOMY; RESEARCH; GRAVITY; PRINCETON UNIVERSITY; COSMIC BACKGROUND EXPLORER (TELESCOPE); SPACE EXPLORATION; GALAXIES; UNIVERSE; COMPUTERS; SIMULATIONS</s>
</P>
